name: PATTERN - Button Glam necklace (pdf)
description:
A piece of flirty glamour.

This necklace is perfect for an evening out. Make it yourself or ask your local bead shop to assemble it for you.

You will receive a PDF-file with all you need for this project: list of materials, tools and step by step assembling instructions. You will also receive a list of photobeads retailers.

Your evening can't be ruined now.

Thanks for stopping by!
